    "author_association": "COLLABORATOR",
    "body": "By designed, you are invited to use the `_beforeTokenTransfer()` hooks to include some custom logic. This hook triggered for calls to `transfer`, `transferFrom`, `send`, `operatorSend`, `burn` and `mint`.\r\n\r\nAdditionnaly, the `_mint` and `_burn` functions are virtual. Still, that might not be enough ...\r\n\r\nCould you tell us more about your usecase?",
